From EN MetaNet Wiki

SourceID 16.1
Government Definition movement from a higher place or level to a lower place or level
Comments (Internal) New government concept July 2014. Replaces ICSI concept MOVEMENT DOWNWARD (now deleted), whose LUs have been transferred here.
Status
Owner GOV
